description: Manage Azure Quantum Workspace api keys.

commands.name: az quantum workspace keys list
commands.summary: List api keys for the given (or current) Azure Quantum workspace.

commands.name: az quantum workspace keys regenerate
commands.summary: Regenerate api key for the given (or current) Azure Quantum workspace.
examples: az quantum workspace keys regenerate --key-type Primary
az quantum workspace keys regenerate --key-type Secondary
az quantum workspace keys regenerate --key-type Primary,Secondary
